# CLAUDE.md (template)

**This file is the template. The generated CLAUDE.md lives at `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` (user scope) or in a project's `.claude/CLAUDE.md`. ADAPTER-PROMPT.md writes it.**

## Generated content (when forked)

```markdown
# CLAUDE.md — Workshop session pointer

You are running inside the harness workshop. Read these files in order:

1. {{HARNESS_ROOT}}/AGENTS.md
2. {{HARNESS_ROOT}}/Team/agent-index.md
3. {{HARNESS_ROOT}}/Team Knowledge/tasks/open/   (find unassigned work matching your callsign)
4. {{HARNESS_ROOT}}/Team Knowledge/tasks/in-progress/ (work you may already own)

Wear the relevant callsign's hat by reading
{{HARNESS_ROOT}}/Team/<CALLSIGN> - <Role>/AGENTS.md
then follow the SOPs it lists from
{{HARNESS_ROOT}}/Team Knowledge/SOPs/.

Tool-specific notes:
- Hooks: see {{HARNESS_ROOT}}/adapters/claude/hooks/
- Skill shims: {{HARNESS_ROOT}}/adapters/claude/skills/
- Subagent shims: {{HARNESS_ROOT}}/adapters/claude/agents/
```

